songs.title: Pizza Girl
songs.lyrics:
[Verse 1]
Love
Showed up
At my door
Yesterday
It might sound cheesy
But I wanted her to stay

[Chorus]
I fell in love with the pizza
Girl
Now I eat pizza everyday
Oh

[Chorus]
I fell in love with the pizza
Girl
Now I eat pizza every day

[Verse 2]
I was stuck
In a box
For so long
Now
I say
That the pizza girl
She's the one for me
Yeah

[Chorus]

[Chorus]
I fell in love with the pizza
Girl
Now I eat pizza
Now I eat pizza
Now I eat pizza everyday
